name: Rejuve MD Anti Age Eye Serum
short_description:
The eyes are often the first area of the face to age, but some also develop under-eye bags and puffiness while others begin to see dark circles and hollows. Rejuve MD eye product the "Complete Eye Treatment" addresses all of these concerns, in addition to the fine lines and wrinkles caused by the breakdown of the skin's supportive matrix. 

The Rejuve MD Complete Eye Treatment contains the bio-identical growth-factors to address lines and wrinkles, plus added active ingredients that target dark circles, under-eye bags and puffiness caused by congestion and fluid retention related to genetics, fatigue, sinus problems and allergies. Safe for sensitive and post-procedure skin, the Rejuve MD system is designed to fit into your existing cleansing and sun protection routine. 

Directions: Apply a small amount around the eye area, twice daily. Allow few minutes for best absorption.

name: Hand MD Restorative Duo
short_description:
Reparative Serum + Anti-Oxidant Rich Moisturizer

A womans hands reveal her age as easily as her face. Hand MD Restorative Duo is an exclusive age-defying dual treatment that helps revitalize, moisturize, and nourish aging dry skin. The anti-aging serum rejuvenates with Retinol and powerful Peptides. The Antioxidant-rich moisturizer deeply hydrates and protects the upper layer of the skin against damage caused by free radicals.

Through extensive research and clinical observation, these two exclusive formulas help reduce the signs of skin aging and protect the hands while working to restore suppleness, moisture and overall skin health.

________

Directions

Press 1 to 2 pumps of serum onto the back of your hand. Rub backs of hands together.

Press 1 to 2 pumps of Antioxidant moisturizer onto the back of your hand. Rub backs of hands together, then rub palms together to distribute remaining product. Use morning and night.

________
Clinical Information

Research shows that most people can accurately guess a womans age just by viewing her hands.

The hands are the workhorses of the body and under constant assault: were gripping a steering wheel, scrubbing dishes, exposing our hands to harsh ingredients and chemicals, and they are in the sun with zero protection.

Hand MD Restorative Duo is two formulations that layer together for a powerful comprehensive effect: a Reparative Serum with potent anti-aging ingredients and an Antioxidant Rich Moisturizing Cream. These two formulas are designed to give the hands a one-two punch against the signs of aging. Our clinical studies were done on women ages 40  65 and resulted in a significant increase in hydration, reduction in fine lines and wrinkles, helped increase skin brightening for the appearance of more even skin tone, and overall radiance.

name: iConix Bluetooth Handsfree Retractable Earphone White
short_description:
Bluetooth Pairing:
1.Keep the distance between the headset and mobile phone within 1 meter.
2.Activate the headset, entered to pairing mode.
3.Initiate Bluetooth of mobile phone (Android: Scan for device), search “Q2” or “Bluedio”.
4.Select “Q2” or “Bluedio” (some mobile phones need to input PIN “0000” as password) and the headset will automatically connect with your phone.
Attention: When headset switch off, keep press the MF button 8 seconds will issue a sound. Generally, there are 120 seconds at maximum to pair headset with your mobile phone, or the headset will power off when the light goes out. Retry steps 1 to 4 to pair again if your operation doesn’t work.

Call waiting:(phone feature)
When phone 1 is in conversation, there is a call for phone 2; Press the MF button once to drop phone 1, and answer a call from phone 2.
Answer a call from phone 2 and keep the call of phone 1: Keep pressing the MF button for around 2 seconds.
Switch back to phone 1: Keep pressing the MF button for around 2 seconds.
Drop call of phone 2, answer the call on phone 1: Press the MF button once.

Multi-point pairing:
Step 1:
Pair phone 1 with headset
a.Keep press MF button 5 seconds to activate headset, light remains bright enters to pairing.
b.Initiate Bluetooth of phone 1, search the headset and pair with it.
Step 2:
Pair phone 2 with headset
c.Keep press MF button 5 seconds to deactivate headset, and switch off BT of phone 1.
d.Keep press MF button 5 seconds to activate headset, LED remains bright, enters into pairing mode.
e.Initiate Bluetooth of phone 2, search the headset and pair with it.
Step 3:
Pair phone 1 with headset again
f. Initiate Bluetooth of phone 1, pair with the headset.
g.Some mobile phone may not reconnect automatically, you may choose the device on Bluetooth list of mobile phone to finish pairing.

name: iConix Micro SD Memory Card 8GB Ultra with Adapter

Iconix Ultra 8GB microSDHC card comes with the plug and play support. This Iconix card by Iconix is compatible with almost all the leading edge devices.The Ultra 8GB Micro SDHC Card by Iconix keeps your music, pictures, and other important documents secure. This 8GB memory card is engineered with the Error Correction code, which detects and corrects errors during data transfer while preventing corruption and loss of your important data. It offers ample space so you dont have to think twice before downloading anything that you want. This Ultra 8GB MicroSDHC card, brought to you by Iconix, comes with an adapter and supports the plug and play system.

Multi Compatibility

This Iconix Ultra 8GB microSDHC card is engineered for perfect compatibility with digital cameras, mobile phones, tablets, and other devices. This memory card has plug and play support so that you can connect it to your PC using a card reader without having to install the drivers.

Ample storage

This Iconix microSDHC card provides ample storage for all your data needs. It is specially engineered for all those who wish to get the most out of their smartphones and cameras.

name: Corded 3000+15pc Ac
short_description: The Dremel 3000 is the result of upgrading our most popular rotary tool using user-requested features to improve the tools design and ergonomics. The tool also features the EZ Twist nose cap with an integrated wrench that allows the nose cap to be used as a wrench to tighten accessories and eliminates the need for a separate wrench. More efficient fan design and side vents provide a cooler running tool making it comfortable for extended periods of use. The tool also features a symmetrical design including a trumpet-shaped nose cap to facilitate a pencil-grip tool hold. The ability to use all existing Dremel accessories and most attachments let the 3000 complete a wide range of applications including cutting, grinding, sanding, carving and polishing a variety of materials. EZ Twist nose cap with wrench for fast accessory changes Variable speed from 10,000 to 33,000 RPM Can be used with all Dremel accessories and most attachments Cool-running ball bearing construction for smooth and quiet operation Replaceable motor brushes extend tool life

name: Biobaby Baby Diapers 16+ KG 34s
short_description:
BioBaby nappies are the nappies with the highest number of biodegradable materials. This helps the environment by eliminating the materials that take the longest to decompose after use, ensuring fewer environmental problems in your babys future.


THE ENVIRONMENT:

Waterproof outer lining  Our diapers are made waterproof by using plastics that will biodegrade within 3 to 6 years.

Packaging  The diapers packaging is made from an oxo-biodegradable material that will biodegrade in 3 to 6 years.

Soft Outer Lining and Anti-leak barriers  Made with oxo-biodegradable materials that kinder to your baby's care and protection, and will biodegrade in 3 to 6 years. BioBaby is the diaper with the highest number sustainable materials (that dont harm the environment), helping us to end our dependency on non-renewable resources and to protect the future resources in your babys world.

Soft Internal Lining and Transfer Layer  Made from natural fibers; to increase sustainability, we have integrated natural and hypoallergenic fibres into the inner lining and transfer layer.

ABSORBENCY:
Natural High-Tech Absorbent Core  The only diaper with a natural high-tech absorbent core lasting up to 12 hours, so that your baby stays dry and comfortable with healthy skin. Confidence and peace of mind, day and night.

Natural Absorbency  The diapers core is made using a formula that integrates sustainable materials suzch as cellulose and a super-absorbent gel made from natural ingredients such as starch,
meaning it biodegrades in less than a year.

COMFORT:

Biobaby has been designed based on export knowledge of babies anatomy, so that your baby can grow and develop with the comfort and freedom of movement. Thats why it has: Adjustable fit and comfort; the diapers soft waist and elastic ribbon naturally adjust to your babys body shape for greater freedom of movement.
